import { Box, HStack, VStack } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import React from 'react'
import Blog from './Blog'

const BlogList = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Box>
        <VStack>
            {/* //set of three docs */}
            <HStack>
                <Blog />
                <Blog />
                <Blog />
            </HStack>
            {/* to be repeated infinitely. */}
        </VStack>
    </Box>
    </>
  )
}

export default BlogList
